content.raw:
I cannot compile this branch in Ubuntu Zesty:


```
#!c++

[  1%] Running protoc on /home/caguero/workspace/ign-msgs/proto/ignition/msgs/wrench.proto
--ruby_out: ignition/msgs/wrench.proto: Can only generate Ruby code for proto3 .proto files.
Please add 'syntax = "proto3";' to the top of your .proto file.
```

Apparently, the use of proto3 is required.
